{"tid":1096541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人好似俾人拉咗入個傳銷group","createTime":"2019-04-07T18:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T05:27:44.000Z","uid":130539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04d229a54fde8335260e99157b746fc8380392af","tid":1096541,"uid":130539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:50:04.000Z","msg":"佢地打俾我，話係wechat send咗條link俾我，叫我入<br />\n咁我就問咩嚟，佢話係啲咩韓國公司會喺香港上市<br />\n有日用品有好多嘢賣，覺得好用仲可以分享出去可以分錢<br />\n間公司叫艾多美 Atomy<br />\n一聽就心諗唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後我直接問「咁咪即係傳銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我就問佢有冇俾錢有冇會費有冇sell嘢，佢地話冇<br />\n話6月先開，咩都未開始，佢想到時買啲日用品咁<br />\n又話冇風險唔使比咩錢，想買就買唔會強迫share出去，唔鐘意都可以30日退款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲send咗條link（簡體）<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/j_nfqJ6BJ0uF7CtKCN15cQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fj_nfqJ6BJ0uF7CtKCN15cQ&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=2560d388\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/j_nfqJ6BJ0uF7CtKCN15cQ</a><br />\n<br />\n我上網google咗間公司，全部都係大陸網，好似冇一個信得過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又話間公司好多地方都有開，遲啲就會香港開<br />\n有啲網話呢間嘢係違法直銷（都係大陸網）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁間公司咁古怪，就叫佢地退出個group<br />\n跟住話想等到6月睇下係咪真係開先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我地識得個係韓國開公司嘅人，我就話你不如去問下佢有冇聽過呢間嘢先<br />\n其實一睇就好古怪，正正經經一間公司邊使搞呢啲，個wechat group有成500人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇人聽過/屋企人都中過招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔明點解一睇就咁奇怪都仲會入去，平時新聞都播唔少啦<br />\n同埋最好留意下屋企人最近有冇比人拉入去啲奇怪group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d59d0d678f3f8ba5448fb8322bcf6f536a08e8","tid":1096541,"uid":130539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:12:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e1d82abc9cd0c3ed2ff0e8224110db29c5f1b0","tid":1096541,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:15:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">覺得好用仲可以分享出去可以分錢</span><br />\n叫屋企人唔好貪小使宜"},{"pid":"4a429389e251682a31ae765f5517cfd8c6fe9996","tid":1096541,"uid":130539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8e1d82abc9cd0c3ed2ff0e8224110db29c5f1b0","tid":1096541,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:15:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">覺得好用仲可以分享出去可以分錢</span><br />\n叫屋企人唔好貪小使宜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:35:37.000Z","msg":"我有，一聽就覺得古古怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿媽都算，估唔到連我阿爸都會陪佢癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65fe8e92186cb1209cc4682830ddf046e49df8b","tid":1096541,"uid":83805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:47:54.000Z","msg":"肯定係傳銷<br />\nFacebook好撚多呢類<br />\n又話乜網絡超市又話韓國野<br />\n又話全世界都好多地方有<br />\n但根本未有人聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲圖全部大陸野咁"},{"pid":"86d0f2c02a53ca57a2e2617bb72ee3e47d25fcdf","tid":1096541,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:54:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">十成十傳銷 ... 樓主小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4af12fed0377a198c7669df53fdd24acb2768dcc","tid":1096541,"uid":130539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c65fe8e92186cb1209cc4682830ddf046e49df8b","tid":1096541,"uid":83805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:47:54.000Z","msg":"肯定係傳銷<br />\nFacebook好撚多呢類<br />\n又話乜網絡超市又話韓國野<br />\n又話全世界都好多地方有<br />\n但根本未有人聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲圖全部大陸野咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:56:59.000Z","msg":"係呀！咩好多地方有連澳洲都有<br />\n但係「大公司」又要用wechat拉人宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好燥底，一陣比人拉都唔知乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fbc992f0bce9e89038de07b6c744dccf12f58b","tid":1096541,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:07:58.000Z","msg":"下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca0992a26b933bffa99d65f15cb464b67d3a371","tid":1096541,"uid":130539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68fbc992f0bce9e89038de07b6c744dccf12f58b","tid":1096541,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:07:58.000Z","msg":"下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T22:10:01.000Z","msg":"唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4d10df3c79da09db9a7393822552062ffbf2d3","tid":1096541,"uid":192893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68fbc992f0bce9e89038de07b6c744dccf12f58b","tid":1096541,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:07:58.000Z","msg":"下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}